279
00:18:59,800 --> 00:19:03,500
It's all thanks to Jiejie's good instruction that Liuzhu is so useful.

280
00:19:04,867 --> 00:19:06,300
If you don't mind me asking,

281
00:19:06,300 --> 00:19:08,133
