334
00:22:58,267 --> 00:23:02,133
All these years, Huanbi and I have been like real sisters.

335
00:23:02,133 --> 00:23:05,286
I won't mistreat her.

336
00:23:05,286 --> 00:23:07,000
Good.

337
00:23:12,333 --> 00:23:14,333
Our miss is a young mistress now.

338
00:23:14,333 --> 00:23:16,433
Yep, she sure is!

339
00:23:16,433 --> 00:23:19,367
