344
00:23:26,700 --> 00:23:28,667
The palace!

345
00:23:28,667 --> 00:23:30,367
I will go wherever our miss goes.

346
00:23:30,600 --> 00:23:31,900
I grew up with her

347
00:23:32,067 --> 00:23:33,833
