is not for just anyone either.

488
00:30:59,200 --> 00:31:01,800
She would need to be in charge of her own Palace 
(where other, usually lesser concubines also reside)

489
00:31:01,833 --> 00:31:04,000
And her rank has to be "Pin" (ranked fifth, above Guiren) and above

490
00:31:04,200 --> 00:31:07,400
Only when she is mistress of her own palace can she reside in its main residence,

491
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:09,033
and manage its daily affairs.

492
00:31:09,033 --> 00:31:11,433
There is but one mistress in every palace,

493
00:31:11,500 --> 00:31:16,800
but there can be an unlimited number of 
Guiren (6th), Changzai (7th) and Daying (8th) in any given palace.

494
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:18,800
Then I have the lowest rank.

495
00:31:18,900 --> 00:31:22,100
Actually no, Daying is not the lowest rank.

496
00:31:22,100 --> 00:31:24,333
The lowest is Guan Nuzi (Serving Women).

497
00:31:24,400 --> 00:31:27,800
I have only heard of the pea sized government official (lit. sesame) ranked 9th,

498
00:31:27,867 --> 00:31:31,100
who knew that the same existed for a Young Mistress in the Harem?

499
00:31:31,300 --> 00:31:34,000
What is a "Servant Lady"?

500
00:31:34,100 --> 00:31:37,100
A Servant Lady is not so different from the serving maids

501
00:31:37,300 --> 00:31:40,300
the only difference being that they can attend His Majesty at night.

502
00:31:40,400 --> 00:31:43,900
If His Majesty likes her, she could be promoted to the rank of Daying.

503
00:31:44,100 --> 00:31:48,000
Custom has it that serving women can only be promoted one rank at a time.

504
00:31:48,033 --> 00:31:50,200
You can't skip a level.

505
00:32:00,632 --> 00:32:04,132
Niangniang, your humble servant greets you respectfully.

506
00:32:04,132 --> 00:32:05,900
Rise

507
00:32:05,900 --> 00:32:07,199
Thank you, Niangniang

508
00:32:07,199 --> 00:32:10,266
Niangniang, The Empress has drawn up the plans for

509
00:32:10,266 --> 00:32:12,132
the new Young Mistresses' residences.

510
00:32:12,132 --> 00:32:14,500
She wanted me to read it to you

511
00:32:14,500 --> 00:32:17,167
If you find anything inappropriate, it can be modified.

512
00:32:18,733 --> 00:32:19,699
All right. Read it.

513
00:32:19,699 --> 00:32:22,900
From the Manchu White Banner, Fucha Guiren will live in the Palace of Lasting Fortune (Yan Xi Gong)

514
00:32:22,900 --> 00:32:26,300
From Mongolian Minor Red Banner, Boerjijite Guiren will reside in the Palace of Essence (Zhong Cui Gong).

515
00:32:26,300 --> 00:32:29,400
From Han Minor Yellow Banner, Shen Guiren will be in the Palace of Whole Blessings (Xian Fu Gong).

516
00:32:29,400 --> 00:32:32,567
From Han Blue Banner, Wan Changzai is in the Palace of Imperial Heritage (Cheng Qian Gong).

517
00:32:32,567 --> 00:32:36,233
What did you say? Wan Changzai?

518
00:32:36,233 --> 00:32:39,100
Yes. Eldest daughter of Zhen Yuandao, Coordinator of Supreme Court

519
00:32:39,100 --> 00:32:41,167
Of all the newly chosen Young Mistresses,

520
00:32:41,167 --> 00:32:44,533
only she received a title. 
Though her rank is not high.

521
00:32:44,533 --> 00:32:47,233
The eloquent one?

522
00:32:47,233 --> 00:32:48,900
Yes. You are correct.

523
00:32:48,900 --> 00:32:53,567
Is this Palace of Imperial Heritage appointed to her by His Majesty?

524
00:32:53,567 --> 00:32:55,367
His Majesty had nothing to do with drawing up the residences.

525
00:32:55,367 --> 00:32:57,333
Everything has been to the directions of the Empress.

526
00:32:57,333 --> 00:33:00,133
The Palace of Imperial Heritage is extremely well situated.

527
00:33:00,133 --> 00:33:03,700
Not only is it large and grand, but it's also close to His Majesty's study.

528
00:33:03,700 --> 00:33:06,633
The Empress really knows how to make His Majesty happy.

529
00:33:06,700 --> 00:33:10,400
She would give him anything for just one word of praise.

530
00:33:10,700 --> 00:33:14,800
She is herself getting along in years,
so she's preparing replacements who will be loyal to her.

531
00:33:15,100 --> 00:33:20,500
The Palace of Imperial Heritage...does she mean for her
to be the sole inheritor of the Imperial attachment?

532
00:33:20,800 --> 00:33:23,500
Let's talk about His Majesty now.

533
00:33:23,567 --> 00:33:27,367
His majesty was the fourth son of the Former Emperor,

534
00:33:27,367 --> 00:33:29,667
Formerly the Prince (Duke) of Yong (Harmonious).

535
00:33:29,800 --> 00:33:31,600
He was married in his Princely Mansion.

536
00:33:31,667 --> 00:33:34,967
The bride was the current Empress Dowager's niece, by a cousin.
(ie., her first cousin once removed; his second cousin)

537
00:33:35,000 --> 00:33:36,500
Of the family Wulanala.

538
00:33:36,700 --> 00:33:40,500
The Duchess was compassionate, wise, and elegant. People adored her.

539
00:33:40,600 --> 00:33:43,100
She and His Majesty were deeply in love.

540
00:33:43,400 --> 00:33:50,100
Unfortunately, three years after their ceremony the Duchess died in childbirth.

541
00:33:50,400 --> 00:33:54,100
The infant prince died as well.

542
00:33:54,100 --> 00:33:58,167
His Majesty is still saddened by the event, even now.

543
00:33:58,167 --> 00:34:01,467
He bestowed upon her posthumously the title Chun Yuan Empress ï¼ˆEmpress of Purity).

544
00:34:01,600 --> 00:34:04,800
It shows how constant our Majesty's affection is.

545
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:09,500
Then the current Empress?

546
00:34:09,700 --> 00:34:12,600
I heard that the Empress is issued from a concubine (shu)?

547
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:16,700
The blessed are not bound by the distinction of "Di" and "Shu."

548
00:34:16,800 --> 00:34:20,800
Her highness the Empress has a virtuous nature, she is the mother of the nation.

549
00:34:21,000 --> 00:34:23,300
I spoke out of turn.

550
00:34:24,733 --> 00:34:28,067
Empress Niangniang is the Empress Chunyuan's s younger sister.

551
00:34:28,200 --> 00:34:31,100
The Empress Dowager appointed her to the then Prince Yong as a duchess-consort.
(one rank beneath the Duchess)

552
00:34:31,200 --> 00:34:33,500
After the death of Empress Chunyuan,

553
00:34:33,533 --> 00:34:36,300
the duchess-consort inherited the Duchess's rank.

554
00:34:36,300 --> 00:34:40,233
His Majesty treats her with courtesy and respect.

555
00:34:42,100 --> 00:34:44,700
Are there any other palaces available?

556
00:34:44,800 --> 00:34:46,000
There is...

557
00:34:46,200 --> 00:34:49,000
the Palace of Jade Fragments (Sui Yu Xuan), where Fang (Fragrance) Guiren used to reside,

558
00:34:49,200 --> 00:34:53,800
is tidy and somewhat refined, but it's a little out of the way,
a bit far and not too big either.

559
00:34:54,000 --> 00:34:55,500
Not too big? It's tiny!

560
00:34:55,800 --> 00:34:57,700
And there is also a stage there formerly used for opera performances.

561
00:34:57,900 --> 00:35:03,400
It only became a residence for the less popular concubines because the Former Emperor thought it too far as a theater.

562
00:35:03,867 --> 00:35:06,000
The location is also said to be unlucky.

563
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:07,900
Unlucky?

564
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:11,200
Just because Fang Guiren was banished to the 
Leng Gong after her miscarriage...

565
00:35:11,400 --> 00:35:12,400
(Leng Gong, lit. Cold Palace; place that concubines who fall out of favor are banished to,
most remain there til death.)

566
00:35:12,500 --> 00:35:13,600
What's the big deal?

567
00:35:13,833 --> 00:35:15,467
If she moves in,

568
00:35:15,500 --> 00:35:19,200
she might even conceive a child like Fang Guiren had done.

569
00:35:19,467 --> 00:35:22,567
Wouldn't that please the Empress even more?

570
00:35:22,567 --> 00:35:23,733
Yes.

571
00:35:23,733 --> 00:35:26,000
Who else lives in the Palace of Jade Fragments?

572
00:35:26,700 --> 00:35:28,067
No one.

573
00:35:28,067 --> 00:35:29,833
Clean it up a little,

574
00:35:29,833 --> 00:35:33,167
Get it ready for Wan Changzai's arrival.

575
00:35:33,500 --> 00:35:36,600
What of that Xia girl?

576
00:35:36,600 --> 00:35:39,200
The one that His Majesty pointed to on a passing whim, 
the one whose name he called "interesting."

577
00:35:39,600 --> 00:35:46,100
Yes, the Empress had to ask His Majesty to make her a Changzai as well,
 because of her father's official rank.

578
00:35:46,300 --> 00:35:49,000
So you think the Empress is inclined to show her favor?

579
00:35:49,200 --> 00:35:50,700
I can't be sure.

580
00:35:51,300 --> 00:35:53,900
Watch her for me.

581
00:35:54,000 --> 00:35:56,000
In case she intends to swear her allegiance to the Empress.

582
00:35:56,300 --> 00:35:59,300
Put her in with Fucha Guiren.

583
00:35:59,400 --> 00:36:02,200
We'll see how her insolence likes that.

584
00:36:02,700 --> 00:36:04,367
But I heard,

585
00:36:04,367 --> 00:36:07,267
His majesty now showers his attention on Hua Fei Niangniang.

586
00:36:07,500 --> 00:36:08,800
Yes, it is so.

587
00:36:08,833 --> 00:36:12,067
Hua Fei Niangniang is the Great General Nian's younger sister.

588
00:36:12,200 --> 00:36:15,500
Her position was already uncontested even while His Majesty was still the Prince of Yong.

589
00:36:15,700 --> 00:36:17,900
But if Hua Fei is indeed so adored by His Majesty,

590
00:36:17,900 --> 00:36:19,500
why hasn't she been granted the title Gui Fei (Noble Consort, 3rd rank)

591
00:36:19,600 --> 00:36:21,100
or Huang Gui Fei (Imperial Noble Consort, 2nd rank) yet?

592
00:36:21,300 --> 00:36:23,200
That brings me to my next point.

593
00:36:23,267 --> 00:36:26,600
The reason is because Hua Fei Niangniang has never borne any children.

594
00:36:26,800 --> 00:36:31,000
So Hua Fei Niangniang was promoted to the rank of Fei (4th rank) without any children?

595
00:36:31,200 --> 00:36:35,100
That's how highly His Majesty regards her.

596
00:36:35,200 --> 00:36:37,300
Of course, His Majesty's affection is not the most important thing,

597
00:36:37,300 --> 00:36:39,933
but conceiving a heir is.

598
00:36:39,933 --> 00:36:44,000
Even a princess is better than no children at all.

599
00:36:44,000 --> 00:36:47,533
Otherwise, you will have absolutely nothing to rely on.

600
00:36:47,533 --> 00:36:52,633
But of course Hua Fei Niangniang still has her youth and health,

601
00:36:52,633 --> 00:36:54,500
plus His Majesty's affection,

602
00:36:54,500 --> 00:36:56,100
so naturally she will have eventual offspring.

603
00:36:56,100 --> 00:36:59,600
I heard that Hua Fei Niangniang's beauty is beyond compare?

604
00:36:59,600 --> 00:37:01,900
She is indeed a celebrated beauty within the Han Banner.

605
00:37:01,900 --> 00:37:05,533
Well, not just in the Han Banners,
but in all of the Eight Banners, the Manchu and the Monglian together,

606
00:37:05,533 --> 00:37:08,600
there is not one who can hold a candle to her.

607
00:37:08,600 --> 00:37:10,700
That is why she is foremost in His Majesty's affections, and his Harem?

608
00:37:10,900 --> 00:37:12,400
Li Bai (poet) once said

609
00:37:12,400 --> 00:37:16,833
How long can you like someone if you only like her appearance?

610
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:22,600
Niangniang, Hua Fei changed Wan Changzai's residence

611
00:37:22,600 --> 00:37:24,133
to the Palace of Jade Fragments (Sui Yu Xuan).

612
00:37:26,133 --> 00:37:29,267
Poor girl.

613
00:37:30,700 --> 00:37:32,900
That place is quite remote,

614
00:37:33,000 --> 00:37:34,500
not to mention extremely plain.

615
00:37:34,500 --> 00:37:36,533
It used to be no more than an opera stage.

616
00:37:36,600 --> 00:37:38,900
Oh, Fang Guiren used to live there!

617
00:37:39,200 --> 00:37:42,400
Hua Fei can be so insolent, making such a change,

618
00:37:42,433 --> 00:37:44,333
without even one word in advance to Your Highness.

619
00:37:44,333 --> 00:37:47,700
You speak of it as if it's something new.

620
00:37:47,700 --> 00:37:50,500
That insolence is exactly what His Majesty likes about her.

621
00:37:53,300 --> 00:37:55,333
Another Grey hair.

622
00:37:58,667 --> 00:38:01,267
Whose nameboard did His Majesty flip tonight?

623
00:38:01,300 --> 00:38:04,900
His Majesty is busy with state affairs today.
He has decided to rest at the Hall of a Resting Soul.

624
00:38:05,300 --> 00:38:06,767
He is likely still awake.

625
00:38:06,800 --> 00:38:08,500
I guess it's just as well.

626
00:38:08,700 --> 00:38:11,100
His Majesty has a fondness for Wan Changzai.

627
00:38:11,100 --> 00:38:14,300
Since the place is so undecorated and obscure,

628
00:38:14,300 --> 00:38:16,567
send some osmanthus trees
(homonymous with "noble")

629
00:38:16,567 --> 00:38:18,667
to ornament it a little.

630
00:38:18,667 --> 00:38:21,267
Rest assured, Niangniang. I will take care of everything.

631
00:38:27,733 --> 00:38:32,800
People always say that once you pass the Palace gates, 

you are forever separated from the life outside.

632
00:38:32,800 --> 00:38:35,600
I'd never expected for it to happen to our family.

633
00:38:36,800 --> 00:38:39,300
Promise you'll take excellent care of yourself.

634
00:38:40,300 --> 00:38:42,600
And be extra cautious with your interactions inside the Harem.

635
00:38:42,700 --> 00:38:44,800
Don't start conflicts and don't involve yourself in disputes

636
00:38:45,000 --> 00:38:49,000
Especially involving the Emperor's favorite, Hua Fei Niangniang.

637
00:38:51,000 --> 00:38:57,400
If, one day, you have the fortune of becoming someone His Majesty esteems highly, then good,

638
00:38:58,600 --> 00:39:02,300
But it's more important to stay alive.
Do you understand?

639
00:39:04,467 --> 00:39:06,333
I will be careful,

640
00:39:07,267 --> 00:39:09,300
so that you will have no reason to be concerned for me.

641
00:39:12,133 --> 00:39:18,100
After I am gone, I'll need you to take care of father and mother, for me as well as yourself,
do you understand?

642
00:39:18,100 --> 00:39:19,633
Yurao understands.

643
00:39:26,200 --> 00:39:29,867
Young Mistress, time is running out.

644
00:39:48,433 --> 00:39:50,433
I have to leave now,

645
00:39:54,267 --> 00:39:57,867
Please take care! Father, Mother!

646
00:40:00,949 --> 00:40:05,466
<i>Thank you for watching! 
<i>Please join us!

647
